    <string name="privacy_policy_title">Privacy Policy</string>
    <string name="privacy_policy_text">
        ER Wait Time Privacy Policy\n\n
        
        This app provides estimated ER wait times at nearby hospitals. We do not collect or store any personal information from users.\n\n
        
        DATA WE COLLECT:\n
        • Location data: We access your location only to show nearby hospitals. This data is used only within the app and is never stored on our servers.\n
        • App usage data: Google may collect anonymous usage statistics to help improve the app experience.\n\n
        
        DATA WE DO NOT COLLECT:\n
        • Personal information: We do not require login or collect any personal information like names, emails, or health data.\n
        • Photos or media: We do not access or collect photos or media files.\n\n
        
        THIRD-PARTY SERVICES:\n
        • Google Maps: Used to display maps and location information according to Google\'s privacy policy.\n
        • Google AdMob: Used to display advertisements.\n\n
        
        CONTACT:\n
        For questions about privacy, contact us at zub165@yahoo.com
    </string>

